org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.operations

Class ParallelDecoder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.operations.ParallelDecoder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the decoded rows
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterator<T>, CloseableIterator<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HBaseParallelDecoder, SimpleParallelDecoder

    public abstract class ParallelDecoder<T>
extends Object
implements CloseableIterator<T>
    An abstract class that offers data stores a way to scan and decode rows in parallel. It is up to the data store implementation to provide implementations of ParallelDecoder.RowProvider to be used for providing rows from the underlying database.

    Note: The row transformer passed in MUST be thread-safe, as decoding happens in parallel.
